title: 820-00928 Wont boot
message:
Hello
I got a 820-00928, it restarts halv way when booting and restarts to question mark. It boots in safe mode but shuts down when starting to copy files, It boots normal from external drive but when tryin to copy files it shuts down. Tried in target mode and it will not copy.

No signs of water dagamage. Any ideas?

title: 820-00928 Wont boot
message:
Looks like SSD issue.
Run SSD test program.

Just in case, clean J9600 contacts.
